Package: CompositionalHDDA
Type: Package
Title: High Dimensional Discriminant Analysis with Compositional Data
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-07-02
Authors@R: person("Michail", "Tsagris", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "mtsagris@uoc.gr")
Maintainer: Michail Tsagris <mtsagris@uoc.gr>
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: Compositional, HDclassif, Rfast, stats
Suggests: Rfast2
Description: High dimensional discriminant analysis  with compositional data is performed. The compositional data are first transformed using the alpha-transformation <doi:10.48550/arXiv.1106.1451>, and then the HDDA algortihm of Bouveyron C. Girard S. and Schmid C. (2007) <doi:10.1080/03610920701271095> is applied. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
